OL,6,FWith just days to go before April's
OL,7,Fprice rises, new research seen by ITV
OL,8,FNews suggests millions of people are
OL,9,Fmissing out on billions of pounds in
OL,10,Ffinancial help.
OL,12,FWater, council tax and energy are just
OL,13,Fsome of the bills set to rise in what
OL,14,Fsome consumer campaigners are calling
OL,15,F"awful April".
OL,17,FYet a large number of customers are
OL,18,Fmissing out on support from "social
OL,19,Ftariffs" , which bring big discounts
OL,20,Ffor those struggling to pay.
